comment: This is the list of Forumoji images.
To add an emoji, it needs an image in the resources/forumoji folder
and a valid hosting link for the Scratch forums,
Add new emojis to the end of this file, or search for a codepoint
or file name to replace an existing one (and remember to update
the hosting link to match the new one).
If the same codepoint is listed twice, the later one will be used.
The emoji list will warn you of duplicate emojis in the console.
